eu.geclipse.core.model
Interface IGridProject

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, IGridContainer, IGridElement
All Known Implementing Classes:
GridProject, HiddenProject
public interface IGridProject
extends IGridContainer

Grid element for projects in the grid model. These projects have not necessarily to be Grid projects but can also be any other type of project located in the workspace. If this is really a grid project, i.e. if isGridProject() returns true, it contains a number of standard folders.
